        {
            "title": "聯邦法官下令美國政府停止計算進口商的IEEPA關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國一位法官下令聯邦政府暫停實施關稅支付流程中的一個關鍵步驟，以便簡化後續的退款流程。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國最高法院;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國最高法院\">美國最高法院</a>推翻了總統唐納德·川普的全球關稅政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周三頒出的裁決中，位於紐約的聯邦貿易法官Richard Eaton下令海關和邊境保護局停止計算川普在進口商報關單上加收的緊急關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他還質疑，政府為何在最高法院裁定此類關稅非法後還要繼續如此操作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Eaton還命令當局重新計算已通過海關程序中上述步驟的特定關稅，移除川普備受爭議的進口稅。這位法官證實，他已被指派處理迄今為止在貿易法院提起的數千起退稅訴訟。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4dfd0a3b-5725-3412-b7d8-1959af6db9fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最高法院上個月推翻川普去年基於《國際緊急經濟權力法》對外國普遍徵收的對等關稅，以及針對中國、加拿大和墨西哥額外徵收的芬太尼相關關稅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：一錘定音 美國最高法院推翻川普對等關稅和針對中加墨的芬太尼稅</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Judge Orders US to Stop Calculating IEEPA Tariffs for Importers</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E8%A8%88%E7%AE%97%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84ieepa%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-210814279.html",
